> <div class=\"content\"> <pre class=\"highlightjs highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash hljs\" data-lang=\"bash\"># In your environment or .env file export OPENAI_API_KEY=&lt;your-openai-api-key&gt;</code></pre> </div> </div> <div class=\"paragraph\"> <p>You can also set this configuration programmatically in your application code:</p> </div> <div class=\"listingblock\"> <div class=\"content\"> <pre class=\"highlightjs highlight\"><code clas\ntableblock\">Property</p></td> <td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\">Description</p></td> <td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\">Default</p></td> </tr> <tr> <td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\">spring.ai.openai.base-url</p></td> <td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\">The URL to connect to</p></td> <td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\"><a href=\"https://api.openai.com\" class=\"bare\">api.openai.com</a></p></td> </tr> <tr> <td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\">spring.ai.openai.api-key</p></td> <td class=\"tableblock halign-left valign-top\"><p class=\"tableblock\">The API Key</p></td> <td class=\"tableblock halign-left valig\nringframework.ai:spring-ai-starter-model-openai' }</code></pre> </div> </div> <div class=\"admonitionblock tip\"> <table> <tr> <td class=\"icon\"> <i class=\"fa icon-tip\" title=\"Tip\"></i> </td> <td class=\"content\"> Refer to the <a href=\"../../getting-started.html#dependency-management\" class=\"xref page\">Dependency Management</a> section to add the Spring AI BOM to your build file. </td> </tr> </table> </div> <div class=\"sect2\"> <h3 id=\"_image_generation_properties\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#_image_generation_properties\"></a>Image Generation Properties</h3> <div class=\"sect3\"> <h4 id=\"_connection_properties\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#_connection_properties\"></a>Connection Properties<